      "span_text": "The TORS surgical technique has been described previously. [CITATION_1] Succinctly, the da Vinci Surgical System (Intuitive Surgical Inc., Sunnyvale, CA) consists of a surgeon's console, a surgical cart, a manipulator unit with two laterally placed instrument arms and a centrally located endoscopic arm holding the three dimensional camera.",
